Adjustable Round Glasses
By Cobold The Fox!
Thanks for supporting me!


To Adjust The Glasses Parameters, change the Parameter values, then right click the Hotkey Node and select "Send Signal".

Parameters:
	GlassesLensSize 
		0 to 1
		Affects the size of the Lens.

	GlassesArmLength
		0 to 1
		Affects the length of the arms.
	
	GlassesArmRotation
		-1 to 1
		Affects the arms position, can be shut or open wider.
	
	GlassesWidth
		0 to 1
		Affects the spacing between the lenses.
